Who: Legacy
Location: Old Maximal Base - makeshift stockade

Legacy stood watching the form of Nightstrike, his single optic
pulsing impassively for a moment as if trying to decide what to do
with the Minion. He stepped over to his to examine him carefully, and
ensure that his restraints were still in place. With a click he
secured them in place and then straightened.

"Tuscon Prime." Legacy's cold voice intoned over an encrypted Autobot
channel, "I am at Nightstike's location. He is unconscious, I will
attempt to wake him."

Legacy looked down at Nightstike as he nudged him with the canon that
served as his left arm. "Awaken." he said in cold imperious tones, "It
would seem that you have questions to answer."

(TAG)

Preston
